{"type": "article", "id": 14838, "title": "马上要上班了，用这 21 个理由骗自己「上班还是很快乐的」！|每天还有一个list", "description": "要相信这都是真的。别哭。", "date": "2015-10-07T13:00:00Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 10822, "name": "上班"}, {"id": 901, "name": "工作"}, {"id": 135, "name": "职场"}, {"id": 3239, "name": "国庆"}], "category": 3, "author": 130547, "comment_count": 63, "praise_count": 371, "image": "img/article/long_show/20160702142633VE8ZMrqhRfDXmtlB.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t<strong>1. </strong><strong> 早睡早起模式重启。</strong><strong>人生因打卡而健康。</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607261422405iepRO6zDblHaqMC.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"461\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"0.7203125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t<strong><strong><strong>2.  </strong>上班就上班。假期的无聊程度难以置信。</strong></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<strong><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726142241vSEdWmRlIGu4pt6q.gif\" width=\"500\" height=\"236\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"0.472\" data-format=\"gif\"></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong>3.  又可以见到那位高颜值女/男同事。已在朋友圈观赏七天。</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong></strong><strong></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702142619e4bs9IFvmZVlziBL.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"720\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<b>4.  跟同事一起吐槽。</b> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702142620e1FEv6iBqgLjYWAp.gif\" width=\"500\" height=\"256\" title=\"4\" alt=\"4\" data-ratio=\"0.512\" data-format=\"gif\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t<strong><b><strong></strong></b></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong><b><strong><b>5.  貌似又有新八卦哦。上班核实一下。</b></strong></b></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong><b><strong><strong></strong></strong></b></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<strong><b><strong><strong><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726142242fTg9uBvIndJQDyxP.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"717\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"0.66388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\"></strong></strong></b></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong>6.  又能见到那个好笑的家伙。</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t<strong></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<strong><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702142621GS1wRc8qYM7u4BaW.jpg\" width=\"512\" height=\"384\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\"></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong>7.  打鸡血/热情/正能量/元气/理想。</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702142622RK1Qe5EruzVbULXj.gif\" width=\"480\" height=\"270\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-format=\"gif\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong>8.  记住，老板就是一种幽默的生物。</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702142622c4iQb9OxuoIEmRCP.gif\" width=\"500\" height=\"281\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"0.562\" data-format=\"gif\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t<strong><strong><strong>9.  八小时而已啦，逛逛淘宝就过去了。对了，</strong></strong>讲真，节后快递都要来了！</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702142623j8YBpeqo51UArOWy.gif\" width=\"500\" height=\"262\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"0.524\" data-format=\"gif\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong>10.  假期经历了好多可怕的事，相亲/亲戚/熊孩子/发飙的老妈……还是上班安全！</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702142624ulqrz8SJ7fGxZNnX.jpg\" width=\"700\" height=\"500\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"0.71428571\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong>11.  公司附近有家餐馆很赞。</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607021426243kDKqFe0TBO7tLhb.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"720\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong>12.  想想办公室有而家里没有的东西……比如咖啡机！</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702142625DP3X52cBtHIRgTNb.jpg\" width=\"586\" height=\"304\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"0.51877133\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong>13.  我司有一只猫/狗。看看它的照片。</strong><span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702142625bvhTe2GWc4XayQgd.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"960\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"0.88888889\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong>14.  补完剧一肚子话想说。终于可以跟那个剧透的同事交流交流。</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702142626yJzaAHIjEc1qbrpg.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"608\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"0.56296296\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t<strong>15.  美容觉睡了七天又变美了。出门让人类瞧瞧。</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702142627wj3c1hMVqd8NSA0P.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"766\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"1.196875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong><strong></strong></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t<strong><strong>16.  赚钱还不开心！？</strong></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702142628RuUDrsJQjwXPhEW2.gif\" width=\"500\" height=\"373\" title=\"现实一点。不上班可赚不到钱。\" alt=\"现实一点。不上班可赚不到钱。\" data-ratio=\"0.746\" data-format=\"gif\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<b><strong><strong></strong></strong></b> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<b><strong><strong><strong><strong></strong></strong></strong></strong></b> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<b><strong><strong>17.  上班 = 减肥。每逢佳节胖三斤。</strong></strong></b> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<b><strong><strong><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726142243Ykza2JZn3pTQvO7R.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"337\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"0.56166667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"></strong></strong></b> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<b>18.  不就是干活嘛？我完全可以用我喜欢的方式干。</b> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<b><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702142628bCkzJ3V01hRFys4p.gif\" width=\"500\" height=\"281\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"0.562\" data-format=\"gif\"></b> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong>19.  他们都说我干活的样子特别酷。</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<strong><img src=\"img/uploads/201607261422439TbVx2mEofzt0ka4.gif\" width=\"500\" height=\"300\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"0.6\" data-format=\"gif\"></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong><strong></strong></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong><strong><strong><strong><strong><strong></strong></strong></strong></strong></strong></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong><strong><strong><strong><strong></strong></strong></strong></strong></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong><strong><strong>20.  星座运程说，我这个月工作会很顺利/得到晋升机会/有艳遇。</strong></strong></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong><strong></strong></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong><strong><strong><strong></strong></strong></strong></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<strong><strong><strong><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702142630vUt3lImjq9BspNaz.jpg\" width=\"900\" height=\"592\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"0.65777778\" data-format=\"jpeg\"></strong></strong></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong><strong></strong></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong><strong><strong><strong>21.  不用催眠。我就是工作狂。</strong></strong></strong></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702142631QygPChLHl5nGVOa0.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"608\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"0.56296296\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}